Rule 1 | Respect
Treat everyone with respect. Any form of disrespect or harassment will result in disciplinary action by a Discord Moderator.

Rule 2 | Language
English is the primary language of this server. Please
communicate in English to ensure inclusivity and make moderation easier.

Rule 3 | Swearing and Bypassing
Swearing and bypassing filters are strictly prohibited. Punishments will be issued based on the severity to maintain a positive and friendly environment.

Rule 4 | Pinging
Only ping others when absolutely necessary. Unwarranted or excessive pinging is not allowed and will result in a warning or punishment.

Rule 5 | Channel Usage
Use the appropriate channels for specific topics. Spamming or misuse of channels disrupts the community and is not tolerated.

Rule 6 | Advertising
Advertising is only allowed in designated channels such as ⁠¦-advertisements. Advertising in other channels or through direct messages is forbidden.

Rule 7 | Explicit Content
Sharing explicit content, including gore, violence, NSFW material, or pornography, is strictly prohibited.

Rule 8 | Personal Information
Sharing personal or private information—whether about yourself or others—is forbidden to ensure everyone's safety.

Rule 9 | Discrimination
Any form of discrimination, including racism, sexism, homophobia, ableism, or hate speech, is not tolerated under any circumstances.

Rule 10 | Suspicious Links
Do not post suspicious, malicious, or scam links. Such actions will lead to immediate penalties.

Rule 11 | Death Threats
Threatening harm or making death threats against anyone is strictly forbidden and will result in severe consequences.

Rule 12 | Punishment Evasion
Evading punishments, such as creating alternate accounts to bypass bans or mutes, is not allowed and will lead to stricter actions.

RULE 13 | Music rule
Do not skip any music without permissions. Inappropriate musics are not allowed, Keep the music appropriate. If you get annoyed from the music, example; Too loud, it is a hard music (much Bass, etc.) And more then let us know about it and we will do the volume low or skip it.

Rule 14 I Ping BoD+
Don't ping our Board of Directors members without a valid reason. Please open a ticket instead. Unnecessary pings may result in a warning.
